{
  "stem": "443.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He said the [INAUDIBLE], the-- the-- the cries and the screams, and the-- it was-- you could hear it miles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So this is what probably happened to him too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He went to-- to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And my youngest sister was with my older three sisters together for a little while in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they selected the youngsters, so they took her away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My other three sisters were sent to labor camps, different camps, different places.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is how they survived.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was sent to a camp about 10 kilometers from Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was called Buna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a camp, about 60,000 people, tremendous camp.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we used to go to work every day.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to put us together, five in a line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to go every morning, used to wake us up early in the morning, it was still dark, because he had to stay in the line for a couple hours because we had to be counted.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every time we came in from work, before you went to work, always had to stay, what it's called, appel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The word appel, I don't know if you've heard of it, is you have to stay and to be counted.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We-- we stayed in that camp for about six months.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I used to go to work every morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I worked as a schlosser.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's called a locksmith.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Locksmith, you know, is not only locks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You could do everything that has to do with steel, with iron.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We used to make pipes because we developed-- we also worked in that place where we established a new factory, so you had to set up the place.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to heat up pipes to be able to connect those machines.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
